Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工智能殖民地和人类的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史的暗面还真藏着不得了的灵异事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们是明白了这些都和狮子堂家有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样下去我们就得考虑我们的步调了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是协助打倒Nerval还是不协助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在作为灵异科卷入这个事件不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再暂时做一下真相的探索不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许能找到和「神秘失踪事件」的关联呢 伊月君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… EX-QT和怪兽…连幽灵都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不知道要调查什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以平民的身份去调查是有限度的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就需要这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 妮娜 这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的ICP证件 再次办理了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那种事做的到吗 伊月可是殉职警官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说是搞错了 混过去手段多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头的家伙们也别那么脑残了行么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就要"不要引起无谓的牺牲"嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们东奔西跑地收集了这么多监视摄影机拍摄的图象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么上头不理睬我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻里也没播放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是装作没发生似的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用把什么都掩盖过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三个死老头子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 茶还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人是原公安来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都受罚降职了 但还真是没用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和我们这边的人员重叠了 超麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以回到ICP了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续安排我到秘侦任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还需要死的话就说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鲁也是 已经不需要外套了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 总觉得很中意这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸物体 退避
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.92,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（致狮子堂 极密）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:59.40,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,290)}{\fs45}{\fad(500,500)}装入箱子里的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨好 狮子堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂竟然不迟到 真是罕见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 前辈最近可是请假的大户呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋帕罗特 要是我出席数不够的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劈了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨好 狮子堂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早晨好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想送到收取物管理科的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但路上边走边想 所以就拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确的说就是箱子 是BOX 是长方体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是送给狮子堂家的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经扫描过确认不是炸弹之类的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包裹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:12.12,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你是狮子堂家的人吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是 是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:20.78,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我希望以交换关于「Enigma」的情报为\N条件让我逃亡 请与狮子堂家总帅传达）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enigma？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是小樱小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在两天内做出这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂家的人一直以来都各自发挥着其作用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梆梆插进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有突然插进来的吗 那个樱馒头！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用奇怪的名字叫我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金绅士主插头插入完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样自我实现达成率已经达到了89%了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要将自己擅自做的部件装到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓自我实现 是用我自己的手来达成才有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到现在不是什么都没做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅只是在使唤秋叶他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别对我说教！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把这个没大脑的家伙赶出去！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香稍微有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是狮子堂评议会的中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂元老院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将人带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我们忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到这个就会想起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢藏 贺统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（乌玛）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 大家 都活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望获得逃亡申请的箱子…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗 说带着Enigma的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:39.01,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（全部只对狮子堂家总帅说）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实关于Enigma的情报是对于狮子堂评议会的最重要的条目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个箱子太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.87,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我是人类）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.15,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（让你看看证据）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:56.68,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（敲门）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲门？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.43,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（敲门！）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女…女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面…真的有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这么窄的地方里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开的话我会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她交由我们保管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人可以回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个人会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然需要评议会的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之是联系ICP让他们领回去什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.03,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这个人不可信）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.08,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（经常听说会在逃亡者不知情的情况下将其处理）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.88,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我作为一个逃亡者要求行动自由）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs22}（由在这时代里所确立的希努克阿姆法 殖民地的建造机关和…）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…由于老是逃课 一点都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在那个箱子里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那么窄…的地方…里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有想呆在里面的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个看起来又窄又挤的箱子里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 觉得外面的世界更加辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的人也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂 你被点名了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能放弃神乐大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要将Enigma夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在在雷欧帕罗特的里面Enigma…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是为了寻找它我们才在这舰内建立了情报系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装着人的箱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将Enigma的情报给风音？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃午饭咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子 箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音音子 你进教室的时候看到这里有个箱子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 No!已经Nothing了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是校内回收巨大垃圾的日子 说不定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分两路去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子 箱子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 狮子堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我调查了下记录 清扫机器人在30分前通过教室前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该往地下的垃圾室去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:46.29,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（是要将我处理了吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 是来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再晚一点的话 你就要在这个处理器里被粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为再利用燃料被回收再利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.67,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（咦~！！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害怕了 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你们知不知道这个值多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂秋叶 你觉得破坏学校的物品会没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在的地方 就会发生奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你这样说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶 白夜 将那个箱子处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知真面目的东西 不能放任其在校内不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等 将这个箱子带到学校里的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有保护她的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"她"？你在说什么啊ICP 不过是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 这里是学生禁止入内的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事由我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比这更安全 而且还能见到姐姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:01.53,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我知道了）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.87,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（那个 刚才）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:10.84,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（谢谢你救了我）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课已经都结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出来了真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 关于这个人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval那里的逃亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval那里的逃亡者？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全封闭箱子里的箱子人呢 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会见一下 现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都进来 进来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走啊跟我走 怦怦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶小姐带来了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个箱子也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想姐姐们马上就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 这里已经安全了 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.42,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不行）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.08,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不行X50）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我想稍微问你一下问题 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从Nerval那里的逃亡者获取证言的机会很珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果获取你的证言的话 也许就可以将「神秘失踪事件」立案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.10,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（明白了 可以）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 首先告诉我你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.47,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（没有名字）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 被Nerval抓住是什么时候的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.75,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（没有记忆）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 因为是箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是部件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval将人类装进箱子 将其作为自己创造的世界的部件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁将Enigma的情报托付给你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.62,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（没有记忆）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出情报后打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:42.13,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（在那之后 在那之后）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.58,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我不知道）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部件不需要记忆与志向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人的时候的回忆也是 在箱子里消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也变得不知道自己是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是部件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类才不是部件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类才不是什么物件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个Nerval到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我们纳米机器人也是有人权保障才被生产出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负这个箱子的人交给警察就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧 伊月小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对…当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我会回到ICP本部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ICP的数据库里也许会留有这位小姐的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取回记忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该会成为解决此次事件的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 在明白什么之前就在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去破解未解之谜吧 箱子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是箱子酱小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这个孩子的名字 因为是箱子所以是箱子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字都没变嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.71,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（箱子酱）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有朋友啊 秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…请…请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…在别人前面做出这样的姿态…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好嘛 这么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.03,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（可爱？？）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:42.60,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（可爱 但是为什么会觉得可爱呢 我不明白）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.40,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（有什么不对吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:54.89,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我觉得我喜欢这个）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在先用这个忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到你从箱子里出来后 大家一起穿着睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来这里一起住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.08,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（嗯）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 箱子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是将人引来狮子堂家的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.40,10,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我什么也没做）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是箱子酱 而且联络地址上也写有这里的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蕾达的目的是将逃走的部件回收与破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放低身子坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很窄 忍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶 听到吗 快到避难所去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然闯进了狮子堂家 就做好了觉悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蕾达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 姐姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是电池坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是吧 在这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到避难所还有五十八米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背着箱子酱去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子酱 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从这里出去 自己走过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子的外面是艰辛的世界哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子的外面没有Nerval
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会引导你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会给予你必须做的事情 生存下去的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 你也能生存下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教母大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子酱！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:14.83,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(495,310)}镜信者们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 把名字想起来也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.82,0:24:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子酱小姐的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴海？泉？岁子？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过别叫我岁子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs20}岁子这名字也有上了年纪的人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那难道是前世的记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.48,0:24:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:31.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空を駆ける 自由に優雅に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:35.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩にも心にも少女は翼を持つ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:38.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生まれ落ちた世界は美しい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:42.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神さえ支配できない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:49.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望(ゆめ)は暗黒に埋められた星で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:53.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見てるだけじゃ輝かず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:57.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私のカラダは宇宙船となり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:00.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考の大気を昇って果てそう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:08.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平穏に甘んじたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:15.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂(ハート)がバグ起こす
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:19.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇあなたのロケットで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:22.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道修正してくださる?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:26.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繋がって確かめ合う
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:32.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私たちアンドロイドじゃないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虹を掛ける 明日へ誰かへ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:39.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願えば届くと少しづつ信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:43.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進んでゆく世界は果て無い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:47.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神にさえ破壊できない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:52.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人が抱えた罪もいつか消えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:31.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由地 优雅的在天空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:35.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女们在肩上和心中都有一双翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:38.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所诞生的这个世界如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:42.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连女神也无法将其支配
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:49.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望被埋在黑暗的星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:53.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅看到却无法闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:57.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们身体化为了宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:00.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好似要升到了思考的大气的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:08.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果甘于平稳的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:15.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂就会产生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:19.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 可以用你的火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:22.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来修正我的轨道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:26.50,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相连接 确认无误
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:32.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是机器人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越彩虹 通向明天 通向谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:39.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果请求就能传到 开始慢慢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:43.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个正在前进的世界没有尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:47.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使连神也无法将其破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:52.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人所背负之罪迟早会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:43.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こころが旅立つのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:49.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰もしらない しらない   星の数にときめいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無敵の好奇心で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:23:01.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君とのりたい のりたい   過去と未来飛ぶシャトル
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:06.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進む 私たちとめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:12.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あしたを変えてみるのもいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:21.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進め 迷いから見つかった答えが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:24.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼んだワクワク感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球でJump！！出会いは銀河の分岐点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:36.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然のいたずらが楽しいんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:41.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いきなりJump！！果て無き宇宙もおともだち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:47.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒険はクセになる そーでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:55.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒険と少女はイコール わかってね！
